{"tid":433780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發，人手置頂］兩對男女野外交歡 叫聲傳偏整個山頭","createTime":"2017-10-12T15:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T05:02:20.000Z","uid":115452,"like":1283,"dislike":307,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"e27895840a7235a235fbba09c040fae9b384f115","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真&middot;標題：「生於亂世，有種責任 」</span><br />\n今日我想講嘅唔係政治野<br />\n而係希望大家正視年輕人自殺問題<br />\n<br />\n連登 高登 香討 <br />\n係香港年青人最集中嘅討論區<br />\n做到咁大型、咁上位嘅討論區<br />\n當然全靠各位搞笑刻薄幽默先咁受歡迎<br />\n<br />\n但去到而家 咁多位學童自殺 <br />\n我地認唔認為而家仲係可以刻薄嘅時候？<br />\n我地講就話讀書唔係唯一出路<br />\n但我地其實口裡不一<br />\n<br />\n升唔到大學就話人連公大都入唔到 係垃圾<br />\n入到公大就笑人冇資格出聲 鯨魚唔係魚<br />\n入到poly city又話人自稱四大係搞笑 冇實力<br />\n入到三大又話而家社會好多大學生 你地冇競爭力<br />\n彷彿人嘅開心要同學歷掛勾<br />\n<br />\n我地一直否定人地嘅努力 <br />\n令到睇我地討論區嘅人都擁有同一個概念<br />\n再加以嘲笑<br />\n結果有日發現自己跟唔上社會扭曲啲期望<br />\n就去死<br />\n<br />\n喂，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地會唔會係殺人兇手？</span><br />\n話：「連登就係咁架啦 唔好睇囉」<br />\n但我地係唔係真係做錯左？<br />\n即使唔係犯法、有自由發表意見嘅權利，但我地係唔係要諗下道德問題？<br />\n<br />\n大型企業都有佢嘅business ethic 要遵守<br />\n從而帶來profit 及令其他企業追隨。<br />\n我地大型討論區係咪都要遵守？<br />\n而今次帶黎嘅benefit就係一條有一條嘅人命、愛、團結<br />\n<br />\n生於呢個扭曲嘅社會<br />\n我地嘅責任就係守護我地香港人 令呢個社會充滿愛 <br />\n互助互愛 亦係香港精神嘅其中一種<br />\n連登有愛 亦係連登其中一種吸引之處<br />\n大家放下屠刀啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw我愛你地<br />\n各位學生 要記得我愛你地<br />\n世界角落總有人愛你地<br />\n你嘅人生 會好精彩架！<br />\n我地一齊再努力少少"},{"pid":"6c74c62c99c01eccb672ea7c39ac7c56b8ebef65","tid":433780,"uid":27777,"like":267,"dislike":15,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"點解你要呃人"},{"pid":"12e38864853e3738c52dfa3ab97f45177dc8ed4d","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":42,"dislike":48,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你要呃人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔心理逐個捉！"},{"pid":"a8ee95dea8520e81df205c5b8c3f5f61b0fa1231","tid":433780,"uid":104658,"like":196,"dislike":5,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"何必呢香港人    開個post都要用假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8778f00e1a96fc12d2555e3b614786155e28652","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":65,"dislike":118,"score":-53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何必呢香港人    開個post都要用假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係你點會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前開過真標題<br />\n冇人理<br />\n想多啲人睇下呢篇野 諗下自己可以點做<br />\n唯有開假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6b9db44c86c80aa18982a0ab41c770eaed8fb5","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3512167a613f5ad37c65d0b7102d12408f655f4","tid":433780,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1991464ea06f244e9fc01b372f0297e821150c12","tid":433780,"uid":28814,"like":9,"dislike":22,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"連登就係咁架啦 唔好睇囉"},{"pid":"8d4fc98b04a7690e485f58da5bd705595892bea6","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":10,"dislike":31,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登就係咁架啦 唔好睇囉</blockquote><br />\n你是殺人兇手嗎？<br />\n今日殺左幾多個？"},{"pid":"dfecffb919a3592d3c0df8fe46bd2bf9eb21dae1","tid":433780,"uid":49955,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"與其呃班學生去努力貢獻社會<br />\n不如教佢哋點樣食窮個仆街政府喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfca539ac20fa0d8bbd83246a22101328e6fd7c2","tid":433780,"uid":123456,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"首先屌一屌樓主for標題<br />\n再支一支持樓主for內文"},{"pid":"fde5507d62c7b3db24c332a97a7303a1d51442d6","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>與其呃班學生去努力貢獻社會<br />\n不如教佢哋點樣食窮個仆街政府喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇教佢地要努力貢獻社會<br />\n我只係想學生知呢到有人愛佢地<br />\n<br />\n另外我主要想講連登兒女唔洗<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去做</span></span>啲咩都救到好多條人命<br />\n只要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔做</span></span>某啲行動就okay"},{"pid":"571247903d277d5ed4cc9f65f0c918829096c30d","tid":433780,"uid":30215,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"按錯<br />\n要正評"},{"pid":"293978cad86879278a43b6349c3abbb0e40ef922","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>按錯<br />\n要正評</blockquote><br />\n連登冇得更改正皮同負皮呢個設定我好唔鍾意"},{"pid":"964693a0b1d65aceaca5d18a69fed649c5f7ce13","tid":433780,"uid":49955,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>與其呃班學生去努力貢獻社會<br />\n不如教佢哋點樣食窮個仆街政府喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇教佢地要努力貢獻社會<br />\n我只係想學生知呢到有人愛佢地<br />\n<br />\n另外我主要想講連登兒女唔洗<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去做</span></span>啲咩都救到好多條人命<br />\n只要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔做</span></span>某啲行動就okay</blockquote><br />\n正能量都害死唔少學生"},{"pid":"8fc9842aaf2d0d27a22f0d4b4587d26ee18c1836","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>與其呃班學生去努力貢獻社會<br />\n不如教佢哋點樣食窮個仆街政府喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇教佢地要努力貢獻社會<br />\n我只係想學生知呢到有人愛佢地<br />\n<br />\n另外我主要想講連登兒女唔洗<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去做</span></span>啲咩都救到好多條人命<br />\n只要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔做</span></span>某啲行動就okay</blockquote><br />\n正能量都害死唔少學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我叫人<span style=\"color: red;\">唔去</span>做啲咩<br />\n唔係叫佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">去</span>撒播正能量<br />\nBtw我重點唔係講緊學生<br />\n係講緊連/高兒女"},{"pid":"01b1cff9a7f9bdbd714ce5f88e0c7cc94666b36c","tid":433780,"uid":93395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"以為係前排同日兩位巴打行山影到既後續"},{"pid":"b013ee124f210a9b60fcb08ae9f6574c0bee9f9a","tid":433780,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"正皮 賣飛佛 上一頁"},{"pid":"59a3527e93ab5b65883d6946552896dfe7a79e52","tid":433780,"uid":14230,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70f625ea3228b5114749a20e551a4235b3069ac7","tid":433780,"uid":130445,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對你個內容冇興趣嘅入咗咪負評上一頁"},{"pid":"1aa5fc0b7355102f2fd41d2c3fbcf862ccf10377","tid":433780,"uid":67278,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>何必呢香港人    開個post都要用假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係你點會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前開過真標題<br />\n冇人理<br />\n想多啲人睇下呢篇野 諗下自己可以點做<br />\n唯有開假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得咁呃人入黎有道德咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1a8a4028358a6e1750cdd83b2e20eeafd612b0","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何必呢香港人    開個post都要用假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係你點會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前開過真標題<br />\n冇人理<br />\n想多啲人睇下呢篇野 諗下自己可以點做<br />\n唯有開假標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得咁呃人入黎有道德咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 希望大家同我一齊變得有道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b1d5bf626af1d10f9d4d59678b1e3503f73d2b","tid":433780,"uid":115452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對你個內容冇興趣嘅入咗咪負評上一頁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但有38個有興趣 <br />\n唔多 但都唔少<br />\n希望救得一個得一個"},{"pid":"a2af53a2e36942351375146d0251bb93dfe392cf","tid":433780,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已